From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Cursor Agent <cursoragent@cursor.com>
Date: Sat, 18 Apr 2026 19:17:41 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(starry/net): add AF_INET6 socket with v4-mapped fallback

Support AF_INET6 TCP/UDP sockets backed by the v4-only stack: normalize
::/::1/::ffff:x.x.x.x for bind/connect, map v4 endpoints back to IPv6
sockaddrs on getsockname/getpeername/recvfrom when the fd was created as
INET6, add IPV6_V6ONLY no-op get/set, track socket domain on the kernel
Socket wrapper, and fix accept() to report the peer address.

Made-with: Cursor

diff --git a/os/StarryOS/kernel/src/file/net.rs b/os/StarryOS/kernel/src/file/net.rs
